♪Sleeves flutter♪

248
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:05,325
♪You sing of love and hate
on high stage♪

249
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:09,498
♪Yearning brings only sorrow♪

250
00:12:09,518 --> 00:12:13,550
♪But in your eyes, I found resolve♪

251
00:12:15,502 --> 00:12:19,318
♪After one final song of parting♪

252
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:23,085
♪We'll meet again only through tears♪

253
00:12:23,086 --> 00:12:26,765
♪Silently, pain blossoms♪

254
00:12:26,926 --> 00:12:30,753
♪In the flames, we embrace♪

255
